    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering 333hp with crisp throttle response via its individual throttle bodies. This example retains its factory 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and M-variable differential lock. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and subframe reinforcement\u2014critical for this chassis. The suspension utilizes a refreshed set of Bilstein dampers paired with OEM bushings to maintain that communicative steering feel. While showing minor cosmetic patina consistent with its mileage, the powertrain remains robust with a linear power delivery up to the 8,000 RPM redline. A driver-focused machine ready for the canyons.",
