    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm looking for a new home for my reliable ride. It's been such a great car for me\u2014well-loved, consistently maintained, and still running like a champ! It\u2019s in really solid shape and is perfect for someone who wants a dependable vehicle without the brand-new price tag. It\u2019s super comfortable and ready for many more road trips. Feel free to reach out if you want to come by and take it for a spin\u2014I think you're going to love how it handles!",
