      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sorted example of the legendary S54-powered platform. The high-revving 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six features individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system, both recently overhauled for optimal volumetric efficiency. Power is delivered through a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission to a variable M differential lock. Crucially, the chassis has been addressed with rear subframe reinforcement plates and the rod bearings have been replaced\u2014essential preventative maintenance for this high-string power plant. The suspension retains its telepathic feedback through refreshed bushings and a precise MacPherson strut/multi-link geometry. While the exterior shows honest patina consistent with a well-loved driver\u2019s car, the drivetrain remains tight and responsive, offering a pure analog experience for the discerning enthusiast.",
